%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor COE as CoE Head

participant UI as WBS Approval UI
participant BFF as Project Planning BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant PPS as Project Planning Service
participant GCS as Governance Consumption Service
participant ADP as Service Adapter
participant DB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias":"Message Bus"}

COE->>UI: Open WBS approval item
UI->>BFF: Load WBS review details
BFF->>ORCH: Get WBS approval view
ORCH->>PPS: Fetch WBS approval details
PPS->>DB: Query project_wbs and approval data
DB-->>PPS: WBS review data
PPS-->>ORCH: Review response
ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show WBS review

alt Approve
    COE->>UI: Approve WBS
    UI->>BFF: Submit approval
    BFF->>ORCH: Start approve flow
    ORCH->>GCS: Check object behavior 
    GCS-->>ORCH: Applicability response
    ORCH->>PPS: Approve WBS and freeze baseline
    PPS->>DB: Update project_wbs_approval = Approved
    PPS->>DB: Update project_wbs status = Approved
    PPS->>DB: Update project_planning baseline_frozen_flag = true
    PPS->>DB: Insert status history
    ORCH->>ADP: Trigger notifications 
    ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish WBSApproved Event
    ORCH-->>BFF: Success
    BFF-->>UI: Show approved state
else Send Back
    COE->>UI: Send back WBS
    UI->>BFF: Submit send back
    BFF->>ORCH: Start send back flow
    ORCH->>PPS: Update status = Sent Back
    PPS->>DB: Update approval record
    PPS->>DB: Insert status history
    ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish WBSSentBack Event
    ORCH-->>BFF: Success
    BFF-->>UI: Show sent back state
else Reject
    COE->>UI: Reject WBS
    UI->>BFF: Submit reject
    BFF->>ORCH: Start reject flow
    ORCH->>PPS: Update status = Rejected
    PPS->>DB: Update approval record
    PPS->>DB: Insert status history
    ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish WBSRejected Event
    ORCH-->>BFF: Success
    BFF-->>UI: Show rejected state
end
